{"tid":678054,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[倒數] 童話online 找回最初的感動","createTime":"2018-05-25T17:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T17:47:48.000Z","uid":99550,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"949916111fcf57fcf4a3505d5da5f3cd105c4f01","tid":678054,"uid":99550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家一齊黎認人! 好多相搵唔番 呢張已經係最多人...<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>2009.06.25 0:13:33<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Hy86NpR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHy86NpR.png&h=1d32b9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2009.06.25 0:14:53<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ilgVyN8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FilgVyN8.png&h=d7bd58b5&s={SIZE}\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">你地提供故事/回憶，我就送錢/道具/寵比你地，或者純傾計都可以!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n* banner [大量收] 各種回憶/故事 密議自出價 +++傾計<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fCpeSg4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfCpeSg4.png&h=fdade943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得 地下室升技 去屎洞升LV 一人一隻木波+金C 去椰子島升lv 一齊打保戰<br />\n一個又一個資料片 解任務去新地圖 由人魚/愛麗絲/.../桃太郎/糖果屋<br />\n到之後2轉 瘋狂練技 黑洞 恩雨 流爆 火衝 獸神 白金卡 幻空拳 鳳翼斬 龍翔閃 獸王劈<br />\n再黎打次元 上23上到行行下訓著都仲行到 地圖都唔洗望<br />\n仲有金大/金小/吉板聚居既你地 大大小小既家族 一齊吹水傾心事 做乜都得<br />\n太多太多既回憶 都已經成為歷史 大家幫手搵番大家既童年回憶啦!<br />\n<br />\n<strong>回到2003 最初的起點...</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eQoaR1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeQoaR1a.jpg&h=15137878&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rLDKESO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrLDKESO.jpg&h=b3ccc302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5HtxE85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5HtxE85.jpg&h=11067d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QNV3D1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQNV3D1a.jpg&h=b7fc59e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NZQkQLM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNZQkQLM.jpg&h=2b33d1e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/E2D6o2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FE2D6o2O.jpg&h=1b144448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位，好好珍惜係童話入面認識既朋友，以後再搵唔番一班咁有童真咁純真既友誼，大家珍重，再見！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>官網 昔日童週</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://fairyland.alta.hk/index/download/index_02.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffairyland.alta.hk%2Findex%2Fdownload%2Findex_02.html&d=Y0dOQ6JPs4jJvYw4c81AVv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5f615610\" target=\"_blank\">http://fairyland.alta.hk/index/download/index_02.html</a>"},{"pid":"681c2d00023a1e0a0a7b50874f095a5fe89bda68","tid":678054,"uid":59587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T17:36:40.000Z","msg":"小五開始玩灰姑娘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路人1 <br />\n愛蜜莉  <br />\n樹根<br />\n你地係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6324f66232318363ad1472f8a9962aecf94c0e93","tid":678054,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd543e39f592db8bd0e3cf07b65b78c6591e230","tid":678054,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T23:05:09.000Z","msg":"R.I.P."},{"pid":"41ec8977401733a72a091183d485a4dae41ccfc4","tid":678054,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T23:34:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27aacb42346a945170c2d08a835d37e8